title: "rule-audit: Static analyzer for LLM system prompts"
abstract: "Pure-Python static analysis tool for AI system prompts. Detects logical contradictions, coverage gaps, priority ambiguities, meta-rule paradoxes, and absoluteness issues. Runs in milliseconds, no LLM dependency, zero API calls."
